00:21:27,910 --> 00:21:30,370
a unique random set of weights.

556
00:21:30,370 --> 00:21:32,440
And that's the
deep-learning aspect of it,

557
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:35,110
is there's depth, there's this
depth wise operation that's

558
00:21:35,110 --> 00:21:36,130
